abstract: Days after a news report focused on conditions at the plant, a California agency said it was investigating an episode that left a millwright’s jaw broken.
snippet: Days after a news report focused on conditions at the plant, a California agency said it was investigating an episode that left a millwright’s jaw broken.
lead_paragraph: Tesla is already under scrutiny because of its uncertain financial outlook, troubles producing a new model and safety questions about its driver-assistance technology.

abstract: The latest celebrity to opt out of an event in Israel over disagreements with its government, Ms. Portman cited her distress over “recent events” in Israel.
snippet: The latest celebrity to opt out of an event in Israel over disagreements with its government, Ms. Portman cited her distress over “recent events” in Israel.
lead_paragraph: JERUSALEM — Natalie Portman, the Oscar-winning actress, has backed out of a major award ceremony meant to honor her in Jerusalem, with her representatives citing her distress over “recent events” in Israel.

headline_main: Why Trump Lashed Out at OPEC: DealBook Briefing

abstract: If New York’s left can keep Andrew Cuomo from striding onto the national stage posing as a progressive, we can send the party a message it needs to hear.
snippet: If New York’s left can keep Andrew Cuomo from striding onto the national stage posing as a progressive, we can send the party a message it needs to hear.
lead_paragraph: After Hillary Clinton’s loss to Donald Trump and Bernie Sanders’s strong showing in the primary, many in the Democratic Party are able to read the writing on the wall: They need to move left. But who wants to step in? Andrew Cuomo, the governor of New York.

abstract: “The Senses: Design Beyond Vision” at the Cooper Hewitt asks visitors to consider sound, taste and smell.
snippet: “The Senses: Design Beyond Vision” at the Cooper Hewitt asks visitors to consider sound, taste and smell.
lead_paragraph: Small and round, Cyrano looks like a portable speaker. But instead of musical playlists, it emits odors in timed combinations — “medleys,” to borrow company-speak — with titles like “Surfside” and “Einstein.”

abstract: MTV’s Video Music Awards will be held at Radio City Music Hall in August as New York City officials seek to lure more awards shows here.
snippet: MTV’s Video Music Awards will be held at Radio City Music Hall in August as New York City officials seek to lure more awards shows here.
lead_paragraph: The administration of Mayor Bill de Blasio has reached an agreement to bring MTV’s Video Music Awards back to New York City this summer — just months after the city saw the return of the Grammy Awards ceremony.
